device -[#0000FF]-> app
mgmt -[#0000FF]-> aaa
mgmt -[#0000FF]-> grpc
aaa -[#0000FF]-> grpc

note top of idb
  **IDB Server - Central Database**
  Unix sockets to all processes
  (/opt/srlinux/var/run/sr_idb_server:50010)
end note

note bottom of xdp
  **XDP Datapath**
  TCP for control plane
end note

legend bottom
  <color:#FF0000>━━━</color> TCP Connection
  <color:#0000FF>━━━</color> Unix Socket
endlegend

@enduml